  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Restaurant &amp; Bar</strong></p>
<p>The restaurant is open for lunch and dinner with an à la carte menu offering traditional Piedmontese cuisine. A small bar is available for drinks during the day and evening.</p>
<p><strong>Spa</strong></p>
<p>The hotel’s large spa boasts a wealth of facilities including an indoor and outdoor pool, Finnish sauna, Jacuzzi and a range of treatments. Facilities and treatments are payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>General Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free parking</li>
<li>Free wifi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
